h-communist-flag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisrn.com%2Fnews%2Fphoto-surfaces-showing-tiktok-executives-posing-with-communist-flag&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=753b0a1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://disrn.com/news/photo-surfaces-showing-tiktok-executives-posing-with-communist-flag</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>TikTok&mdash;Yes, TikTok&mdash;Is the Latest Window Into China&rsquo;s Police State</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/tiktok-is-the-latest-window-into-chinas-police-state/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftiktok-is-the-latest-window-into-chinas-police-state%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=6f3ebfd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/tiktok-is-the-latest-window-into-chinas-police-state/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係有班廢青死都要用TikTok<br />\n但其實都有美國後生仔識理性分析聽人講 <br />\n佢地只係之前唔知支共D衰野<br />\n比多D source 比D耐性 (唔好一味屌) 有D都會聽你講<br />\nTikTok = Bytedance = CCP = human right abuse = genocide<br />\n<br />\n成功例子:<br />\n有一個原本仲話我係propaganda 之後自己話humbled <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8a0Q90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8a0Q90.jpg&h=ac1cf44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOQcHgF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOQcHgF.jpg&h=08f54a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyKXTom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyKXTom.jpg&h=e4f86235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d72ffa7ec1bad08197b51f2b83cb3513542441f","tid":2179650,"uid":122275,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:29:59.000Z","msg":"本身美國人都笑9班tiktok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d375c5a0f0184046f9b444e7c3104ed313c8c0","tid":2179650,"uid":270889,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"quote":{"pid":"1d72ffa7ec1b